{"tid":2351802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜：可能採取更嚴格防疫封鎖措施","createTime":"2021-01-03T14:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T15:02:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04125493feb5280a9c00a18af90c476b1326c610","tid":2351802,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568410-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568410-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0P3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=08e4b61a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568410-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c6e8b654\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568410-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜接受英國廣播公司訪問時表示，為了控制不斷蔓延的疫情，英格蘭地區可能要採取更嚴格的防疫封鎖措施，目前仍未清楚四級防疫封鎖措施所帶來的影響，有需要繼續觀察是否需要推出其他額外的措施。<br />\n<br />\n在疫苗方面，英國在星期一開始為民眾接種牛津大學及阿斯利康研發的疫苗，首批疫苗有53萬劑，約翰遜希望在三個月後，完成接種數千萬劑。<br />\n<br />\n另外，原定明日開學的倫敦等地區的學校，將會推遲，改為網上上課，但英國部分地區的學校會如期在明日開學，約翰遜相信，學校是安全的地方，強調接受教育的重要性。目前英國部分地區屬於最高級別的四級防疫封鎖之中，禁止不同家庭之間的聚會，餐廳、酒吧、咖啡店要關閉。"},{"pid":"dbba6f7005be65a5434ecd58e06a34f8eb838d66","tid":2351802,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係咪會移民去法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892ff20ae66ef8ee00b0ed0f11c8bd571e1cacac","tid":2351802,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbba6f7005be65a5434ecd58e06a34f8eb838d66","tid":2351802,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係咪會移民去法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"bdc0661d36ed1f3f4961cffe8fa885936cddd13d","tid":2351802,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"民眾：開party"},{"pid":"dddd66988b7fe1dd3c6aa11cb0c349d41de73fdc","tid":2351802,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc0661d36ed1f3f4961cffe8fa885936cddd13d","tid":2351802,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"民眾：開party"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EquRTG7XEAAF7eQ?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEquRTG7XEAAF7eQ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=dea2e35d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90223392941dffaf5c3ef2d7d047c7eeaa56358b","tid":2351802,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddd66988b7fe1dd3c6aa11cb0c349d41de73fdc","tid":2351802,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc0661d36ed1f3f4961cffe8fa885936cddd13d","tid":2351802,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"民眾：開party"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EquRTG7XEAAF7eQ?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEquRTG7XEAAF7eQ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=dea2e35d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"一波差過一波，歐洲都封佢入境"},{"pid":"2d45ee8add8a96a38e36ff5bf2442363a802c4d9","tid":2351802,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"電影Doomsday的場景<br />\n只不過係,今次係成個英格蘭、威爾斯和蘇格蘭被封鎖"}]}